* European Trip of CA River Plate 1961

 

 
 
*14.06.1961      Madrid          Real Madrid             2-3     River Plate
*18.06.1961      Napoli               SSC Napoli                 1-6   River Plate
*21.06.1961      Milan                    Internazionale               1-1   River Plate
*24.06.1961      Turin                                                 Juventus          2-5     River Plate
*29.06.1961      Sevilla                                                                 Sevilla         3-2     River Plate

 
 
*Match details
 

6/14/1961; Real Madrid            ; 2-3;     River Plate     ; Chamartín, Madrid; C.Lo Bello
Di Stéfano 6, Di Stéfano 15; Roberto 5, Roberto 48, Delem 30
Real Madrid:            J.Alonso (R.Domínguez); Miche, Santamaría; Casado, Pachín Vidal (Ruiz), Mateos; Herrera, Del Sol, Di Stéfano, Puskas, Gento.
                                 
River Plate:                                         Carrizo; O.Rodríguez, Ramos Delgado; Echegaray, J.Varacka, Schneider; D.Pérez (Villagarcía), Moacyr, Pepillo, Delem (Sarnari), Roberto.
                                                              

 
6/29/1961; Sevilla FC             ; 3-2;     River Plate             ; Sánchez Pizjuán, Sevilla; J.Pardo Hidalgo
Oliveros 30, Rivera 39, Idigoras 80; A.Rojas 17, Pepillo 25
Sevilla FC:             Mut; Juan Manuel (Santin), Campanal (Maraver); Valero, Ruiz Sosa (Luque), Achucarro (de La Torre); Oliveros, Rivera, Idigoras, Antoniet, Agüero (Muñoz).
River Plate:                                          Carrizo (Ovejero); O.Rodríguez, Decio; J.Varacka, Echegaray, Salvador (N.López); D.Pérez, Moacyr, Pepillo (Delem), A.Rojas (Sarnari), Roberto.


